{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember, when I climbed up on the bunk, I saw icicles coming from the rafters, right over my bunk, a little slightly off over.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I chopped them down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And two days later-- there must have been a leak in the roof.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, the moisture froze, and we-- I was getting icicles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So every few days, I would just knock them down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then later, they would come back again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just incredibly cold and nasty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- Well, the winters in Poland are notorious for being nasty and very long winters, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, with the hunger and everything else, there was not much-- nothing, there was not much here, I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I do remember one scene, which sort of stuck in my mind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When we came out of the showers and got dressed and were aligned on that-- on that place, that square, right inside the camp, and when we came out dressed like in those strange uniforms, suddenly, we looked at one another, and we burst out laughing.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I do remember my brother's friend, Leon, was standing right in front of me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he turned around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were already in rows of five.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He turned around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the two of us just-- I mean, I never laughed so hard in my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this happened to everybody else, because the comical clothing that we wore, it was absolutely--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Looking at each other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it [? was ?] like a stage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was simply a theater, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
